id=sip-server
name=Embedded SIP Server (call/SMS bridge) [UNDER DEVELOPMENT]
version=v0.1.0-dev
versionCode=1
author=kaandikec
description=⚠ UNDER DEVELOPMENT. Tiny static SIP server (~2.4 MB statically linked Go) on UDP/5060. Pairs with the on-device F50SipBridge app (com.f50.sip) plus companion phones/laptops to forward SMS-over-SIP and call signaling. Auth via MD5 Digest; localhost registrations bypass auth. Users + passwords in /data/sip-server/sip_users.conf. Hard-dep: bin-utils v1.3.0+. Soft-dep: ims-voice-fix (without it, observed cellular calls die at the F50's screen-off timeout, ~20 s). End-to-end voice test pending.
updateJson=https://raw.githubusercontent.com/dikeckaan/magisk-zte-f50-sip-server/main/update.json
